/*------------------------------------------------------------------------
    File        : XmlSerializableException
    Purpose     : Exception thrown by the XmlSerialable class during
                  serialization and deserialization
    Syntax      :
    Description :
    Author(s)   : Mike Fechner / Consultingwerk Ltd.
    Created     : Sat Mar 14 13:27:00 CET 2015
    Notes       :
